<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />I wait in silence for God alone;</para>

<para style="q1">for my hopes are set on him.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />He alone is my rock and my salvation;</para>

<para style="q1">he is my high tower; I will not be moved.</para>
